---
// Newsletter signup component in Lenny's style
---

<div class="email-signup">
	<h3>Join 500,000+ subscribers</h3>
	<p>Get the weekly digest of insights on product, growth, and career development.</p>
	<form class="email-form" action="#" method="post">
		<input 
			type="email" 
			class="email-input" 
			placeholder="Enter your email" 
			required 
			aria-label="Email address"
		>
		<button type="submit" class="btn">Subscribe</button>
	</form>
	<p class="disclaimer">No spam, unsubscribe anytime.</p>
</div>

<style>
	.disclaimer {
		font-size: 12px;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-top: 12px;
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
</style>